Done. Both `transcript.json` (schema-validated, 25 iterations, 32 hypotheses, 29 analyses) and `analysis_summary.txt` are written in the bundle directory.

**Headline finding:** A clean three-way logical-AND interaction. Response is ~16-17% in seven of the eight cells of the (feature_001 × feature_014 × feature_021) joint table; only the all-three-positive cell jumps to 63.3%. The signal is captured by a single product term (logit coef +2.13, OR ~8, p < 1e-90); each of the three features is necessary and they are functionally symmetric.

**Refined treatment-effect subgroup:** `feature_001=1 AND feature_014=1 AND feature_021=1 AND feature_026=0 AND feature_009=0` — n=1,790 (3.6% of cohort), response 78.6% vs 16.5% outside (RD +62 pp, OR ~19). Either suppressor (feature_026 or feature_009 set to 1) abolishes the entire benefit (triple × suppressor interaction coefs ≈ −2.5, both p < 1e-40). `feature_004` adds a constant prognostic gradient on top (response 86% / 77% / 67% across levels 0/1/2 within the subgroup) but does not modify the triple effect. Age (feature_011, 18-92) and all other binary/continuous features showed no treatment-effect modification.
